e:T70b,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Postwise better than SEO.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Postwise scores 6.0 overall while SEO.ai scores 7.0. Postwise is best for Twitter/X threads and LinkedIn posts, while SEO.ai excels for SEO-optimized content and content scoring."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Postwise or SEO.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Postwise starts at $29/mo and SEO.ai starts at $49/mo.  SEO.ai offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Postwise to SEO.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Postwise and SEO.ai support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Postwise vs SEO.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Postwise holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. SEO.ai has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Postwise for purpose-built for twitter/x and linkedin and SEO.ai for real-time seo scoring as you write."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Postwise or SEO.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend SEO.ai for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Postwise remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize purpose-built for twitter/x and linkedin. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$e"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"contain