18:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Postwise and SEO.ai share a solid foundation of core features including Short Form, Templates, Tone Control. On the other hand, SEO.ai uniquely offers Long Form and Seo Tools and Multilingual and Team Collaboration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Postwise holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while SEO.ai scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
19:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Postwise offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $29/mo, compared to SEO.ai's starting price of $49/mo. SEO.ai stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Postwise requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
