1c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Postwise is best suited for Twitter/X threads, LinkedIn posts, social media growth, personal branding, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. SEO.ai, meanwhile, shines for SEO optimized content, content scoring, keyword targeting, SEO teams, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2022, Postwise describes itself as \"AI ghostwriter for Twitter/X and LinkedIn content.\" SEO.ai, established in 2022, positions itself as \"AI-first SEO writing tool with real-time optimization scoring.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
1d:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **SEO.ai** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0), more features (7 vs 3), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Postwise is a poor choice — far from it. Postwise excels in its own right, particularly for Twitter/X threads and LinkedIn posts.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value real-time seo scoring as you write, go with SEO.ai. If purpose-built for twitter/x and linkedin matters more to you, Postwise is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
